body:
Hey guys, as promised a couple of days ago, i uploaded part 2/2 of a 1v1v1 walls match with vladthegreat100 and thecreator!

This video is just over 4 minutes long, and it's really exciting!

Anyways, I hope you guys enjoy this video!

*Please note that I am not advertising Vlad's server. He downloaded this map very quickly and we played on it just for fun. There is no IP given, and the server is not even ready yet. This was just for a quick fun match, and I have no intention of advertising his server.*

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OJ_4n11gtaI

Thanks guys,
-Porky.
